<div class="master-container">
    <div class="image">
        <%= image_tag "logo.png", size: "80x80" %>
    </div>
    <div class="purpo">
        <%= link_to 'My Dashboard', dashboard_index_path, :id => 'hover-purp' %>
    </div>

    <div class="purpo2">
        <%= link_to 'Analytics', dashboard_analytics_path, :id => 'hover-purp' %>
    </div>

    <div class="purpo">
        <%= link_to 'My Settings', dashboard_settings_path, :id => 'hover-purp' %>
    </div>

    <div class="container-main-dash">
        <div class="headz">
            <h1>Dashboard</h1>
            <h3>Welcome <%= current_user.fname.capitalize %> <%= current_user.lname.capitalize %> to your store <%= @business_stores.name.capitalize %>!</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="mini-container">
          <h2> <%= @business_stores.name.capitalize %> </h2>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed quis pretium massa, nec vulputate quam. Morbi porta vitae quam quis condimentum. Vivamus vitae eros et velit varius elementum vel in lacus. Donec sit amet sagittis felis. Donec vehicula massa sed augue faucibus interdum. Etiam nec accumsan orci. Nunc hendrerit, sem nec tincidunt ornare, turpis sem venenatis sapien, eget tincidunt tellus nisi ac dolor. Nam id tincidunt sapien, eu iaculis nunc.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mini-container-2">

        </div>

        <div class="client-container">
          <div class="client-container-info">
            <h2>Currently</h2>
            <h3>14</h3>
            <h2>NotifiQ users</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="weather-container" id="weather-container" data-latitude="<%= @business_stores.latitude %>" data-longitude="<%= @business_stores.longitude %>">
          <div class="weather-container-info">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">

                <div id="weather-icon">
                </div>

                <div id="info">
                </div>

            </div>

                <div id="city">
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="logout">
        <%= link_to 'Log out', destroy_business_user_session_path, method: :delete, :id => 'logz-out' %>
    </div>
</div>


